{"tid":550775,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外判背後","createTime":"2018-02-05T05:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T05:58:25.000Z","uid":121464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fd60cbb8980bac32f3154fea62c639e6b43f2ec3","tid":550775,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T05:22:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=252941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D252941&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBupUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=91e324f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D252941&h=db17737b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=252941</a><br />\n<br />\n連月以來，多間清潔承辦商被揭共用辦公室、董事或持有人共同持有其他公司。<br />\n<br />\n上月初，《經緯線》記者收到線報，指有兩間清潔承辦商關係密切，亦懷疑有交替中標。不過，翻查商業登記署、公司註冊處文件，以至過去清潔承辦商活動資訊及其他公開文件，均未見兩間公司有明顯關係。<br />\n<br />\n於是，記者將調查方向改由兩間承辦商現時或過去曾服務的屋邨入手，透過多種渠道，收集承辦商在邨內的相關紀錄，最終發現，同一時期兩間承辦商分別於不同屋邨派出的代表，姓名竟是一模一樣，遂打開偵查缺口。<br />\n<br />\n今集《  #經緯線 》會揭開兩間外判清潔承辦商箇中關係。<br />\n<br />\n足本重溫<br />\n第一節：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2E3rVw4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2E3rVw4&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBupUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=37b68211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2E3rVw4</a><br />\n第二節：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2GOJLAi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GOJLAi&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBupUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=6dd8f5c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2GOJLAi</a><br />\n <br />\nsource: now 新聞"},{"pid":"98c52709763490a7fd380a9a2b3d2608eb6275c0","tid":550775,"uid":31330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T05:58:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C5MBVUFDPcg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC5MBVUFDPcg&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBupUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=f68f7b32\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C5MBVUFDPcg</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}